title: "agentic-patterns: reference implementations of core agentic AI patterns"
abstract: >-
  Twelve core agentic AI patterns implemented as runnable, tested reference code
  in Python, each covered from its canonical form through 2025-2026 research.
  Every example runs offline against a deterministic scripted provider with no
  API key.
